snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - First Trailer (2026) Chris Evans, Robert Downey Jr | Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— robert downey jr

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, Avengers: Doomsday positions itself as the opening act of the Multiverse Saga’s final confrontation, where Victor von Doom rises as a master of science and sorcery who believes the multiverse must be controlled to be saved. As Earth’s heroes stand divided, Sam Wilson’s Captain America attempts to rebuild the Avengers while rival teams and uneasy alliances complicate any hope of unity. The arrival of the Fantastic Four from another reality and the long-awaited emergence of the X-Men signal that the conflict can no longer be contained within a single universe. With incursions threatening to collapse entire timelines, Doom’s ideology challenges heroes and gods alike, drawing figures like Loki into a battle over who truly holds the right to shape existence. The story frames Doomsday as a turning point where legacy, power, and sacrifice collide, setting the stage for a multiversal reckoning that will define the future of the Marvel universe.

snippet.title: SQUARE UP - jamie paige x peak divide feat. GUMI & rachel lake
snippet.description:
"oh, i swing for the light!"

HEY GUYS I DID A SONG FOR THE GAME UNBEATABLE
i've been watching this game's development since the very beginning - some of the main people who worked on it i've been friends with for almost 15 years! - and it is an indescribable honor to have been able to put my own little touch on it. i'm serious when i say i think it might be my favorite game i've ever played? certainly in terms of how it made me feel. it's so fucking good guys please play it i am a changed woman

--

UNBEATABLE AVAILABLE NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2240620/UNBEATABLE/
(IT'S ON PS5 AND XBOX TOO I THINK)
ALSO FOLLOW D-CELL GAMES ON BSKY: https://bsky.app/profile/dcellgames.com
ALSO CHECK OUT THEIR WEBSITE: https://www.unbeatablegame.com/

bandcamp & streaming will be added soon!! we're still working out the details of all that, but once it's up, i'll add a pinned comment with details

inst/svp/etc: https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fo/hytbdtcth431749z4h9ba/AA2lu1g7j_T4OMFre-eHJrk?rlkey=hr1b428au5lpkwchi7hoychi1&st=xpq9kfnc&dl=0
(svp includes rachel's part!)

human vocals by rachel lake
https://bsky.app/profile/rachel.dcellgames.com
synthesized vocals by megpoid GUMI
(but also kasane teto is doubling rachel's lead vocals in the chorus and she's pretty loud so maybe she counts as a lead vocalist too? i dont know. this was intended to be a beat/gumi yuri fanfic so of course teto is there. as for whether she's a lead vocalist or not, idfk the good folks at vocadb will figure it out for me)

art by:
ricedeity - https://ricedeity.online/
BEARVAMPS - https://twitter.com/BEARVAMPS
mv edited by jamie paige (omg thats me)
music by peak divide and jamie paige
https://bsky.app/profile/peakdivide.bsky.social
https://bsky.app/profile/jamies.page
https://jamies.page/

peak divide is clara maddux and vasily nikolaev
https://bsky.app/profile/postergirlxoxo.bsky.social
https://bsky.app/profile/vastonik.bsky.social

also rj lake was there. he wrote two lines of the chorus too? but his most meaningful contribution might've been making me substantially less nervous during our creative discord calls by distracting me with the dumbest shit imaginable. also idk where else to bring this up but did you know he drew the jamie paige logo? the 'jamie paige!' wordmark that's my banner on bandcamp and the logo at the beginning of this video. he made that ten years ago and i haven't had a single reason to change it because its honestly perfect. thank you rj. you're an incredible artist and a lovely friend and you scare the living hell out of me. i hope this is a sufficiently funny way to credit you
https://bsky.app/profile/rj.dcellgames.com

--

lyrics:
a mark upon an unlit sky
the fire reflected in your eyes, i
can't even fathom how it's been so long
or that our wishing could have been so wrong
the callouses have all gone soft
suppose i never fought that often
but there's a bullet kept inside my zone
in case you ever think to come and own it

don't waste my time on a lie
if you want me, try me, come and surprise me
oh, i swing for the light

square up, god i'm tired of waiting
can't you say somethin' i don't already know?
square up, 'cause the daylight is fading
am i too fast or have you just gotten slow?
i hit record and blow out the mic
just counting down the seconds 'till the time of my life
so square up, get the hell in the ring
i don't want another reason 'til you're bleeding, baby

(BEAT SOME ASS!)
(BACK TO BACK!)
'cause my fist flies fast, so fast
(BEAT SOME ASS!)
(BUILT TO LAST!)
i'll keep it comin' to the end

[LOCK IN, LOCK IN]
[IF YOU LOCK IN YOU CAN DO ANYTHING]

a mark upon an unlit sky
a bitter little bruised reminder
there was a time i couldn't take that blow
your hand extended so i don't stay solo
the scars upon my hands laid bare
if only you could fight so fairly
we could've had another friendly bout
now i won't stop until you spit your teeth out

don't waste my time, just put up a fight!

square up, god i'm tired of waiting
can't you say somethin' i don't already know?
square up, 'cause the daylight is fading
am i too fast or have you just gotten slow?
i hit record and blow out the mic
just counting down the seconds 'till the time of my life
so square up, get the hell in the ring
i don't want another reason 'til you're bleeding, baby

just waste my time for a while
i've been wanting, waiting, stuck in a daze
i'm lonely, take me
five fingers clenched in a fist
begging, please, just try me, come and surprise me
oh, i swing for the light

#megpoid 
#gumi

https://live.smosh.com Smosh Hospital is a live streamed parody of a classic hospital drama, where the cast is continually surprised by last minute line changes, prop mishaps and improvised bits designed to make everyone break character. If they break or make a mistake, they get replaced by their double - creating a rotating cast of characters and annihilating the show!

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

I discuss the new clips in the promo which showed Vecna going after Holly and Max, Kali helping Eleven and Hopper inside The Upside Down, and the theory of Steve or Dustin's death. Ok so the Avengers Doomsday trailer has just leaked and though it’s a cinema exclusive I have seen it and want to talk about everything it revealed. I dont wanna do any long intro I just want to get into the teaser


Im nice like that

We’ve sat through the comic cons, we’ve sat through five hours of chairs and now the trailer is finally here. Doomsdays one of those films ive been eagerly waiting for and it’s kinda been on a crazy journey over the last half decade. Now I dont care what anyone tells you mate…I dont care how many videos people make about how Doctor Doom was the plan all along and he was there in the background and this was all some genius plan mate. That isnt the case. Unless like you think the plan was to announce Avengers Kang Dynasty and then have Jonathan Majors go through his court case and then get fired. Which yeah if that was the plan.

snippet.title: Normal - Official Teaser Trailer (2026) Bob Odenkirk, Henry Winkler, Lena Headey
snippet.description:
Watch the teaser trailer for Normal, an upcoming movie starring Bob Odenkirk, Henry Winkler and Lena Headey.

For Sheriff Ulysses (Odenkirk), his provisional posting to the quaint Midwestern American town of Normal was meant to be a welcome respite from both his marital woes and recent moral injuries in the line of duty. But when a botched bank robbery interrupts the municipality’s tranquil pace, a dark secret is inadvertently exposed, and Ulysses soon discovers that the town is anything but its namesake.

The latest collaboration between Bob Odenkirk, John Wick creator Derek Kolstad and Nobody producer Marc Provissiero, director Ben Wheatley’s (Free Fire, High Rise) kinetic neo-Western stars Odenkirk as an unassuming substitute sheriff with a troubled past who, after moving to a small, sleepy town, responds to a bank robbery and unknowingly uncovers something far more explosive.

Normal is produced by Marc Provissiero, Bob Odenkirk, and Derek Kolstad in partnership with QWGmire. Molly C. Quinn, Matthew M. Welty, and Elan Gale, along with Josh Adler, Rhonda Baker, Carrie Wilkins, Glenn Feig, Matthew J. Anderson, Jared D. Underwood, Andrew C. Robinson, and Ellen Rutter serve as executive producers. Normal is written by Derek Kolstad and directed by Ben Wheatley.

Normal opens in theaters nationwide on April 17, 2026.

#IGN #Normal #ActionMovie

(light, star, lambs), heavenly angels,
and the warm, joyful world of the Santa Village.

reimagined through AI cinematic art and a

snippet.title: Percy Jackson and the Olympians Season 2 | Trailer 2 | Disney+
snippet.description:
After Camp Half-Blood’s borders fall, Percy Jackson sails into the treacherous Sea of Monsters to rescue Grover and recover the Golden Fleece, the only hope for Camp Half-Blood. With Annabeth, Clarisse, and Tyson at his side, Percy must survive sirens, Polyphemus, and the deadly passage of Scylla and Charybdis, all while Luke rallies an army to awaken Kronos and destroy Olympus. Heroes don’t run; they fight for each other and their home. Season 2 of Percy Jackson and the Olympians streams now on Disney+ and Hulu.
